’Ł@a09297c3843d8b8c1deb0445ad80f889b9ffdc5235a55fadb287d04c625b7526ŁĘTitle: title: to yaml
Path: Examples
Content:
Outputs a YAML string representing the contents of this table.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[foo bar]; ["1" "2"]] | to yaml
- foo: '1'
  bar: '2'


```
